class="section-title">
<span>6.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=hire-employees>Hire employees.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-hair-salon-section6-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=build-the-ideal-candidate-persona>Build the ideal candidate persona.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-the-ideal-candidate-persona-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Build the ideal candidate persona."></div></div><p>Because a good team will drive success in your business, it's important that you hire quality candidates. Ideally, you should be looking for experience, a cosmetology license, a range of skills and knowledge, a willingness to learn, and a positive attitude.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-hair-salon-section6-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>6.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=create-a-detailed-job-description>Create a detailed job description.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-job-description-288x288-20200818_2020-08-18-144212.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Create a detailed job description."></div></div><p>Your job description should include a detailed description of the type of candidate you're looking for, which qualifications and skills are required, and a list of daily job responsibilities. Once you've found potential candidates, follow up with an interview, practical assessment, and background checks.</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 512 512" style="enable-background:new 0 0 512 512;" xml:space="preserve">
<g>
