"},{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Separate different areas using plinths, pot plants, or different floor levels.<\/p>\n"}]}]},{"@type":"HowToSection","position":"6","name":"<p>Hire employees.<\/p>\n","itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"1","name":"<p>Build the ideal candidate persona.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Because a good team will drive success in your business, it's important that you hire quality candidates. Ideally, you should be looking for experience, a cosmetology license, a range of skills and knowledge, a willingness to learn, and a positive attitude.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-hair-salon#how-to-start-a-hair-salon-section6-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-the-ideal-candidate-persona-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Create a detailed job description.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Your job description should include a detailed description of the type of candidate you're looking for, which qualifications and skills are required, and a list of daily job responsibilities. Once you've found potential candidates, follow up with an interview, practical assessment, and background checks.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-hair-salon#how-to-start-a-hair-salon-section6-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-job-description-288x288-20200818_2020-08-18-144212.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>All new and re-hired employees must be reported to the new hire department in your state. This must be done <strong>within 20 days<\/strong> of employment.<\/p>\n"}]}]},{"@type":"HowToSection","position":"7","name":"<p>Market your hair salon.<\/p>\n","itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"1","name":"<p>Create a website.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>A must-have for every modern business is a website. Your website should be user-friendly, informative, and perfectly aligned with your brand. To save on costs, there are many website builders that have free versions and are packed with templates to help you get started.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-hair-salon#how-to-start-a-hair-salon-section7-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-a-website-288x288-20200818_2020-08-18-144748.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Pay-per-click advertising and optimizing your website for search can also have huge payoffs, but you'll either need to research these topics or hire a local agency to help you.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Leverage social media.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Never overlook the power of social media. Facebook and Instagram lend themselves nicely to salons. Just remember that the point of social media is to actively participate in it. This means you'll need to be accessible to your customers, share relevant pictures, videos, and memes regularly and freely.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-hair-salon#how-to-start-a-hair-salon-section7-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-leverage-social-media-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"3","name":"<p>Register your business with Google.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>These days people most often find businesses by asking their phones about it. If you want to appear when someone asks \"where is the nearest hair salon?\" Be sure to register for Google My Business. Also, consider setting up a Yelp! page and asking happy customers to rate your business there.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-hair-salon#how-to-start-a-hair-salon-section7-step3","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-register-with-google-288x288-20200818_2023-09-25-161053_ovnv.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}}]}]}</script> <div
